org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN versions ON versions.id = issues.fixed_version_id WHERE issues.fixed_version_id IS NOT NULL AND issues.project_id <> versions.project_id AND versions.sharing <> 'system' AND (versions.project_id IN (1, 5, 6, 3, 4) OR issues.project_id IN (1, 5, 6, 3, 4))

rewrites.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id WHERE issues.fixed_version_id IS NOT NULL AND issues.project_id IN (1, 5, 6, 3, 4)
